org.ftcbootstrap.components.utils

Class TelemetryUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ftcbootstrap.components.utils.TelemetryUtil

  • public class TelemetryUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class for standard opmode.telemetry feature Utilities include: 1) Adding data does not send to the Driver station display until issuing a second sendData command. This allows you to organize all of your telemetry data before sending them out 2) adds timestamps to the data'
